15. Rd1 cxd4 16. cxd4 Rc8
{ Black now wins a pawn, but White gets excellent compensation @@StartBracket@@White's attack being worth more than a pawn@@EndBracket@@. }
17. f4 gxf4 18. Nxf4 { Black has a weak king and a lot of problems here, e.g. }
18... Bxc4 19. O-O Qg5 20. a4 O-O
{ 20...Bb3  21.Rde1  Bxa4  22.d5  e5  23.Nh5+- } 21. Nh5
{ White has a strong attack. } *

