{ Black doesn't want to give up space, but now he no longer plays on the weakness of White's c4 pawn @@StartBracket@@since, of course, White can now exchange his c4 pawn whenever he wants@@EndBracket@@.We do not have a different type of pawn structure and for this variation, but also for a general understanding of this pawn structure. }
