15. Rd1 e5
{ White got what he wanted. White's knight now gets a great @@StartBracket@@monstrous!@@EndBracket@@ spot @@StartFEN@@r2qk2r/p2n1ppp/1p1pp3/n1pP4/Q3P3/P1P2PN1/6PP/R1BR2K1 b kq - 3 15@@EndFEN@@  15...Qe7?  protecting the d6-pawn leads to a terrible position for Black  16.dxe6  fxe6  17.Bf4 }
