16... h3 17. e4
{ We have here a couple of grandmaster games which have continued with  17.g4  or  17.gxh3  .  I would like to propose a novelty. White doesn't mind allowing  17...hxg2  because he would then put his rook on the g-file thus supporting the attack. }
