{ White has very good attacking prospects, although the computer obviously holds! }
18... Nh5
{ This position is sharp, White has good attacking prospects. The variations I will give unless you study this course and are able to remember them, are not likely to be found in OTB play. }
19. Rxg2
{ For readers who want to investigate further, I recommend looking at  19.f4  or  19.Bc1 }
19... Ne7 20. Nh6+ Kf8 21. e5
{ For a human this position looks like a slaughterhouse, but engines are resourceful! }
