Qf5 { Surprisingly, White doesn't have more than a draw. } 23... Qh4 24. Ng5+
Kg8 { 24...Ke7  25.Qf7+  and White is winning. } 25. Qh7+ Kf8
{ White can still put Black to a test. } 26. Rg3 Ke7
{ The only move, with the idea of bringing the rook into play. } 27. e6 Rh8 28.
Qf5 Nf6 { Threatening ...Qxh2+ } 29. Kf1 { And all ends peacefully. } 29...
