{ Black has the tactical resource 21...Nxe4 which saves him.@@StartFEN@@rnr3k1/pp1b2pp/4pB2/2q5/4PN1P/2n2PQ1/6P1/R3KB1R b - - 2 20@@EndFEN@@  20...g6  seems more logical, but White can exchange queens and have a good chance to attack.  21.Qf2  Qxf2  22.Kxf2 }
21. Nh5 { And now Black saves his skin. } 21... Nxe4 22. fxe4 Qb4+ 23. Kf2
{ Draw by perpetual check:  23...Qc5+  24.Ke1  Qb4 } *

